Project Manager Buy Side (Investment Management, Proj Man
Project Manager Buy Side (Investment Management, Proj Man
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
Salary:  GBP620 - GBP700 per day + expensesProject Manager Buy Side (Investment Management, Project Management, Buy Side, Asset Management, Delivery, Programmes, Charles River, stakeholder management)
Global consultancy is looking for a Project Manager to work on the delivery of of Charles River and other Investment Management solutions for their client onsite at their Head Office in Abu Dhabi.
The Project Manager will be responsible for the delivery of multiple, business critical projects, for investment & asset management solutions within the business. The Project Manager will be involved in the stakeholder management, understanding requirements, resource allocation, workshops and getting the projects completed on time and to budget.
The suitable candidate MUST have come from a proven Project Management background delivering Investment Management, Asset Management or Buy Side solutions for clients. In depth knowledge of Investment Management, Project Management, Buy Side, Asset Management, Delivery, Programmes, Charles River, stakeholder management is key. Excellent interpersonal and communication skills are essential.
